<li><a href="/wiki/Equifinality" title="Equifinality">Equifinality</a>&#160;– Principle in systems theory</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Scientific_method" title="Scientific method">Scientific method</a>&#160;– Interplay between observation, experiment, and theory in science</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Syncretism" title="Syncretism">Syncretism</a>&#160;– Combination of beliefs and traditions</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Tree_of_knowledge_system" title="Tree of knowledge system">Tree of knowledge system</a>&#160;– Map of history from Big Bang to present</li>
